ing-own-major-issues-3749643">英国一些较小的音乐场所“经营不善”</a> ，并驳回了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-case-has-been-made-for-a-1-ticket-levy-on-all-arena-gigs-for-the-survival-of-grassroots-venues-and-artists-3611533">对所有演出场地大小和规模的演出征收 1 英镑门票费的呼吁。多于</a>。</p><p>作为回应， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-say-manchester-co-op-live-arena-comments-were-disrespectful-and-disingenuous-and-call-on-1-ticket-levy-to-save-uk-talent-pipeline-3749732">音乐场所信托基金会首席执行官马克·戴维德（Mark Davyd）告诉<em>NME</em> ，他认为罗登的言论“无礼和持久”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-hit-back-at-manchesters-co-op-live-for-saying-some-grassroots-venues-are-poorly-run-despite-arena-facing-own-major-issues-3749643">，</a>同时也强调了讽刺的讽刺意味由于许多后勤问题，场地被迫推迟发布。</p><p>从那时起， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-say-manchester-co-op-live-arena-is-a-great-idea-but-urge-them-to-work-in-a-way-that-secures-the-future-of-live-music-3752713">音乐场所信托基金会（MVT）表示，新的合作社现场竞技场是“一个好主意”，但敦促老板“以确保现场音乐的未来的方式工作”</a> 。</p><p>尽管 Co-Op Live Arena 一直存在问题， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-owners-of-manchesters-co-op-live-are-planning-the-greatest-arena-in-the-world-for-london-3751598">但其所有者仍计划在伦敦建造“世界上最伟大的竞技场”</a> 。此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-music-venue-moles-in-bath-closes-after-45-years-today-is-a-very-sad-day-3553756">一些历史悠久的草根场馆被迫关闭</a>，其中许多场馆仍面临永久关闭的威胁。</p><p>合作社的现场竞技场说，他们“找到一种方法来帮助使它正确”，在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/co-op-live-arena-say-theyre-finding-a-way-to-help-make-it-right-with-frustrated-and-out-of-pocket-fans-after-show-cancellations-3753307">表演取消后，他们沮丧且自付费用的粉丝</a>。</p> ;
随着任天堂取消8,535个项目，GitHub将开发人员与法律资源连接到法律资源https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/github-connecting-devs-with-with-legal-esources-asource-as-nintendo-takes-down-down-8535-project-projects-3753299？连接devs-with-legal-resources-a nintendo-takes-takes-down-8535项目Ali ShutlerFri, 03 May 2024 11:27:00 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsNintendo https://www.nme.com/?p=3753299 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="超级马里奥RPG。学分：任天堂。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这是我们致力于开发人员的承诺的一部分”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/github-connecting-devs-with-legal-resources-as-nintendo-takes-down-8535-projects-3753299">随着任天堂取消8,535个项目，GitHub将开发人员与法律资源联系起来，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="超级马里奥RPG。学分：任天堂。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Super-Mario-RPG-Nintendo-Switch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/brands/nintendo">任天堂</a>大规模下降后，Github将许多开发商指示法律资源，该公司影响了8000多个项目。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/princess-peach-showtime-review-nintendo-3603934">“桃子公主：Showtime！”评论：让观众想要更多</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">Nintendo Switch Switch</a> Emulator Yuzu被迫关闭， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-switch-emulator-yuzu-shuts-down-must-pay-1-9million-3596876">开发商热带雾霾要求为任天堂支付190万英镑</a>作为和解协议的一部分。</p><p> Yuzu及其团队一直反对盗版。我们出于对任天堂及其游戏机和游戏的热情而真诚地开始了这些项目，并且不打算造成伤害。但是我们现在看到，由于我们的项目<a href="https://twitter.com/yuzuemu/status/1764733659444064671" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可以</a>规避任天堂的技术保护措施，并允许用户在授权硬件之外玩游戏，因此它们导致了广泛的盗版。 Nintendo的背面目录无法合法购买现代游戏机。</p><p>本周早些时候，任天堂提交了一次DMCA取消通知，该通知针对使用Yuzu代码创建的GitHub项目，其中8,535个项目受到影响（通过<a href="https://torrentfreak.com/one-nintendo-dmca-notice-just-wiped-out-8535-yuzu-emulator-forks-240502/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TorrentFreak</em></a> ）。</p><p> <a href="https://github.com/github/dmca/blob/master/2024/04/2024-04-29-nintendo.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Github</a>在任天堂回来了，分享了公众回应，以<a href="https://docs.github.com/en/github/site-policy/dmca-takedown-policy#a-how-does-this-actually-work" target="_blank" rel="noopener">解释</a>开发人员平台“联系了家长存储库的所有者，以使他们有机会进行更改”，然后再禁用与此删除通知有关的任何内容。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">哇，任天堂今天向 Yuzu 的 github 分支/克隆发布了超过 8500 个 DMCA。 <a href="https://t.co/A0Q3yZVLUt">pic.twitter.com/a0q3yzvlut</a></p><p> -  Sujano先生（@mrsujano） <a href="https://twitter.com/MrSujano/status/1785917730073256363?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年5月2日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Github还“向所有受影响的存储库所有者提供了有关如何<a href="https://docs.github.com/en/articles/guide-to-submitting-a-dmca-counter-notice" target="_blank" rel="noopener">提交DMCA反通知的</a>信息，并提出将所有受影响的存储库所有者与<a href="https://github.blog/2020-11-16-standing-up-for-developers-youtube-dl-is-back/#developer-defense-fund" target="_blank" rel="noopener">法律资源</a>联系起来，这是我们为开发人员提供支持的一部分。”</p><p>该平台<a href="https://github.com/github/dmca/blob/master/README.md#anatomy-of-a-takedown-notice" target="_blank" rel="noopener">补充说：</a> “知道Github和开发人员有机会和声音倡导法律和公共政策的变化，以更好地支持软件开发。” </p><figure id="attachment_3446373" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3446373" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3446373" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Tears-of-the-Kingdom.jpg" alt="塞尔达传说：王国之泪" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Tears-of-the-Kingdom.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Tears-of-the-Kingdom-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Tears-of-the-Kingdom-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Tears-of-the-Kingdom-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Tears-of-the-Kingdom-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Tears-of-the-Kingdom-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3446373" class="wp-caption-text">塞尔达传说：王国之泪。学分：任天堂</figcaption></figure><p>作为对尤祖（Yuzu）的案子的一部分，任天堂声称，在正式释放之前的几周中<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-legend-of-zelda-tears-of-the-kingdom">，Zelda的传奇：王国的眼泪</a></em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/nintendo-claims-tears-of-the-kingdom-was-pirated-a-million-times-before-official-release-3594376">被盗用了一百万次</a>。</p><p>最近，被取消的<em>门户64</em>